"\"https://rancherdesktop.io\">Rancher Desktop</link> 等容器运行时"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:104
msgid ""
"The <literal>SL-Micro.x86_64-6.0-Base-GM2.raw</literal> OS image file must "
