"This guide assumes an existing RKE2 cluster and Rancher (including cert-"
"manager) has been installed, for example by using Edge Image Builder (<xref "
"linkend=\"components-eib\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"本指南假设已安装现有的 RKE2 群集和 Rancher（包括 cert-manager），例如已使用 "
