#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:125
msgid ""
"It can take around two minutes for the init container to run on this "
"deployment, so ensure the pods are all running before proceeding:"
msgstr "大约要经过两分钟，init 容器才会在此部署中运行，因此请确保所有 Pod "
