#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:553
msgid ""
"All of the SUSE Edge 3.2.1 components, including dashboard extensions, are "
"distributed as OCI artifacts. To install SUSE Edge Extensions you can use "
"Rancher Dashboard UI, Helm or Fleet:"
msgstr ""
"所有 SUSE Edge 3.2.1 组件（包括仪表板扩展）均作为 OCI 制品分发。要安装 SUSE "
"Edge 扩展，可以使用 Rancher Dashboard UI、Helm 或 Fleet："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:554
msgid "Installing with Rancher Dashboard UI"
msgstr "通过 Rancher 仪表板 UI 安装"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:555
msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Extensions</emphasis> in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis> section of the navigation sidebar."
msgstr ""
"单击导航侧边栏 <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis>（配置）"
"部分的 <emphasis role=\"strong\">Extensions</emphasis>（扩展）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:556
msgid ""
"On the Extensions page, click the three dot menu at the top right and select "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Manage Repositories</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"在“Extensions”（扩展）页面上，单击右上角的三点菜单，然后选择 <emphasis role="
"\"strong\">Manage Repositories</emphasis>（管理储存库）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:557
msgid ""
"Each extension is distributed via its own OCI artifact. Therefore, you need "
"to add repositories for each extension that needs to be installed."
msgstr "每个扩展都是通过自身的 OCI "
"制品分发的。因此，您需要为需安装的每个扩展添加储存库。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:558
msgid ""
"On the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Repositories page</emphasis>, click "
"<literal>Create</literal>."
msgstr ""
"在 <emphasis role=\"strong\">Repositories</emphasis>（储存库）页面上，单击 "
"<literal>Create</literal>（创建）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:559
msgid ""
"In the form, specify the repository name and OCI artifact URL, and click "
"<literal>Create</literal>."
msgstr "在表单中指定储存库名称和 OCI 制品 URL，然后单击<literal>创建</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:560
msgid ""
"Akri Dashboard Extension Repository URL: <literal>oci://registry.suse.com/"
"edge/3.2/akri-dashboard-extension-chart</literal>"
msgstr ""
"Akri 仪表板扩展储存库 URL：<literal>oci://registry.suse.com/edge/3.2/akri-"
"dashboard-extension-chart</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
