"安装扩展后，Rancher UI 会提示重新加载页面，如<literal><link xl:href=\"https"
"://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.10/integrations-in-rancher/rancher-"
"extensions#installing-extensions\">安装扩展 Rancher "
