msgid ""
"An AMD64/Intel 64 physical host (or virtual machine) running SLES 15 SP6 or "
"openSUSE Leap 15.6"
msgstr "一台运行 SLES 15 SP6 或 openSUSE Leap 15.6 的 AMD64/Intel 64 "
"物理主机（或虚拟机）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:724
msgid ""
"A copy of the SUSE Linux Micro 6.0 RAW image found <link xl:href=\"https://"
"www.suse.com/download/sle-micro/\">here</link>"
