msgstr "从储存库提取最新的 chart："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:936
msgid ""
"Install SUSE Storage in the <literal>longhorn-system</literal> namespace:"
msgstr "在 <literal>longhorn-system</literal> 名称空间中安装 SUSE Storage："

