"Additional components (<xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-how-"
"additional\"/>)."
msgstr "其他组件（<xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-how-additional\""
"/>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1217
msgid ""
"During the upgrade process, the Upgrade Controller continually outputs "
"upgrade information to the created <literal>UpgradePlan</literal>. For more "
"information on how to track the upgrade process, see Tracking the upgrade "
"process (<xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-how-track\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"在升级过程中，升级控制器会持续向创建的 <literal>UpgradePlan</literal> "
"输出升级信息。有关如何跟踪升级过程的详细信息，请参见<xref linkend"
"=\"components-upgrade-controller-how-track\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1218
msgid "Operating System upgrade"
msgstr "操作系统升级"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1219
msgid ""
"To upgrade the operating system, the Upgrade Controller creates SUC (<xref "
"linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller\"/>) Plans that have the "
"following naming template:"
msgstr ""
"升级操作系统时，升级控制器会创建命名模板如下的 SUC（<xref linkend"
"=\"components-system-upgrade-controller\"/>）计划："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1220
msgid ""
"For SUC Plans related to control plane node OS upgrades - <literal>control-"
"plane-&lt;os-name&gt;-&lt;os-version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>."
msgstr ""
"对于与控制平面节点操作系统升级相关的 SUC 计划 - <literal>control-plane-&lt"
";os-name&gt;-&lt;os-version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1221
msgid ""
"For SUC Plans related to worker node OS upgrades - <literal>workers-&lt;os-"
"name&gt;-&lt;os-version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>."
msgstr ""
"对于与工作节点操作系统升级相关的 SUC 计划 - <literal>workers-&lt;os-"
"name&gt;-&lt;os-version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1222
msgid ""
"Based on these plans, SUC proceeds to create workloads on each node of the "
"cluster that perform the actual OS upgrade."
msgstr "SUC "
"会根据这些计划，继续在执行实际操作系统升级的群集的每个节点上创建工作负载。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1223
msgid ""
"Depending on the <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal>, the OS upgrade may "
"include:"
msgstr "根据 <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal>，操作系统升级可能包括："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1224
msgid ""
"Package only updates - for use-cases where the OS version does not change "
"between Edge releases."
msgstr "仅软件包更新 - 适用于操作系统版本不随 Edge 版本变动的使用场景。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1225
msgid ""
"Full OS migration - for use-cases where the OS version changes between Edge "
"releases."
msgstr "完整操作系统迁移 - 适用于操作系统版本随 Edge 版本变动的使用场景。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1226
msgid ""
"The upgrade is executed <emphasis role=\"strong\">one</emphasis> node at a "
"time starting with the control plane nodes first. Only if the control-plane "
"node upgrade finishes will the worker nodes begin to be upgraded."
msgstr ""
"升级首先从控制平面节点开始，一次执行<emphasis role=\"strong\""
">一个</emphasis>节点的升级。只有在控制平面节点的升级完成后，工作节点才会开始"
"升级。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1227
msgid ""
"The Upgrade Controller configures the OS SUC Plans to do perform a <link xl:"
"href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_drain/"
"\">drain</link> of the cluster nodes if the cluster has more than <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">one</emphasis> node of the specified type."
msgstr ""
"如果群集有<emphasis role=\"strong\">多个</emphasis>指定类型的节点，"
"升级控制器会配置操作系统 SUC 计划来<link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_drain/\""
">清空</link>群集节点。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1228 l10n/source/edge.xml:1237
msgid ""
"For clusters where the control plane nodes are <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">greater than</emphasis> one and there is <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">only one</emphasis> worker node, a drain will be performed "
"only for the control plane nodes and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"对于控制平面节点<emphasis role=\"strong\">有多个</"
"emphasis>而工作节点<emphasis role=\"strong\""
">只有一个</emphasis>的群集，只会清空控制平面节点，反之亦然。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1229
msgid ""
"For information on how to disable node drains altogether, see the "
"UpgradePlan (<xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-extensions-"
"upgrade-plan\"/>) section."
msgstr ""
"有关如何完全禁用节点清空的信息，请参见“UpgradePlan”（<xref linkend"
"=\"components-upgrade-controller-extensions-upgrade-plan\"/>）一节。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1230
msgid "Kubernetes upgrade"
msgstr "Kubernetes 升级"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1231
msgid ""
"To upgrade the Kubernetes distribution of a cluster, the Upgrade Controller "
"creates SUC (<xref linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller\"/>) Plans "
"that have the following naming template:"
msgstr ""
"升级群集的 Kubernetes 发行版时，升级控制器会创建具有以下命名模板的 SUC（"
"<xref linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller\"/>）计划："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1232
msgid ""
"For SUC Plans related to control plane node Kubernetes upgrades - "
"<literal>control-plane-&lt;k8s-version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>."
msgstr ""
"对于与控制平面节点 Kubernetes 升级相关的 SUC 计划 - <literal>control-"
"plane-&lt;k8s-version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1233
msgid ""
"For SUC Plans related to worker node Kubernetes upgrades - <literal>workers-"
"&lt;k8s-version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>."
msgstr ""
"对于与工作节点 Kubernetes 升级相关的 SUC 计划 - <literal>workers-&lt;k8s-"
"version&gt;-&lt;suffix&gt;</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1234
msgid ""
"Based on these plans, SUC proceeds to create workloads on each node of the "
"cluster that perform the actual Kubernetes upgrade."
msgstr "SUC 会根据这些计划，继续在执行实际 Kubernetes "
"升级的群集的每个节点上创建工作负载。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1235
msgid ""
"The Kubernetes upgrade will happen <emphasis role=\"strong\">one</emphasis> "
"node at a time starting with the control plane nodes first. Only if the "
"control plane node upgrade finishes will the worker nodes begin to be "
"upgraded."
msgstr ""
"Kubernetes 升级将从控制平面节点开始，一次升级<emphasis role=\"strong\""
">一个</emphasis>节点。只有在控制平面节点的升级完成后，工作节点才会开始升级。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1236
msgid ""
"The Upgrade Controller configures the Kubernetes SUC Plans to perform a "
"<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/"
"kubectl_drain/\">drain</link> of the cluster nodes if the cluster has more "
"than <emphasis role=\"strong\">one</emphasis> node of the specified type."
msgstr ""
"如果群集有<emphasis role=\"strong\">多个</emphasis>指定类型的节点，"
"升级控制器会配置 Kubernetes SUC 计划来<link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_drain/\""
">清空</link>群集节点。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1238
msgid ""
"For information on how to disable node drains altogether, see <xref "
"linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-extensions-upgrade-plan\"/>."
msgstr ""
"有关如何完全禁用节点清空的信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-"
"controller-extensions-upgrade-plan\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1239
msgid "Additional components upgrades"
msgstr "其他组件的升级"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1240
msgid ""
"Currently, all additional components are installed via Helm charts. For a "
"full list of the components for a specific release, refer to the Release "
"Notes (<xref linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"目前，所有其他组件都是通过 Helm chart "
"安装的。有关特定版本各组件的完整列表，请参见发行说明（<xref linkend"
"=\"release-notes\"/>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1241
msgid ""
"For Helm charts deployed through EIB (<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/>), "
"the Upgrade Controller updates the existing <link xl:href=\"https://docs."
"rke2.io/helm#using-the-helm-crd\">HelmChart CR</link> of each component."
msgstr ""
"对于通过 EIB（<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/>）部署的 Helm chart，"
"升级控制器会更新每个组件的现有 <link xl:href="
"\"https://docs.rke2.io/helm#using-the-helm-crd\">HelmChart CR</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1242
msgid ""
"For Helm charts deployed outside of EIB, the Upgrade Controller creates a "
"<literal>HelmChart</literal> resource for each component."
msgstr ""
"对于在 EIB 之外部署的 Helm chart，升级控制器会为每个组件创建一个 "
"<literal>HelmChart</literal> 资源。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1243
msgid ""
"After the creation/update of the <literal>HelmChart</literal> resource, the "
"Upgrade Controller relies on the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/"
"helm-controller/\">helm-controller</link> to pick up this change and proceed "
"with the actual component upgrade."
msgstr ""
"在创建/更新 <literal>HelmChart</literal> 资源后，升级控制器会依赖 <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/helm-controller/\">helm-controller</"
"link> 来拾取此更改并继续执行实际的组件升级。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1244
msgid ""
"Charts will be upgraded sequentially based on their order in the "
"<literal>ReleaseManifest</literal>. Additional values can also be passed "
"through the <literal>UpgradePlan</literal>. If a chart’s version remains "
"unchanged in the new SUSE Edge release, it will not be upgraded. For more "
"information about this, refer to <xref linkend=\"components-upgrade-"
"controller-extensions-upgrade-plan\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Chart 将按照 <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> 中的顺序依次升级。您还可通过 "
"<literal>UpgradePlan</literal> 传递其他值。如果在新 SUSE Edge 版本中某个 "
"chart 的版本保持不变，则不会将其升级。有关这方面的详细信息，请参见<xref "
"linkend=\"components-upgrade-controller-extensions-upgrade-plan\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1245
msgid "Kubernetes API extensions"
msgstr "Kubernetes API 扩展"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1246
msgid "Extensions to the Kubernetes API introduced by the Upgrade Controller."
msgstr "升级控制器引入的 Kubernetes API 的扩展。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1247
msgid "UpgradePlan"
msgstr "UpgradePlan"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1248
msgid ""
"The Upgrade Controller introduces a new Kubernetes <link xl:href=\"https://"
"kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/"
"\">custom resource</link> called an <literal>UpgradePlan</literal>."
msgstr ""
"升级控制器引入了一个名为 <literal>UpgradePlan</literal> 的新 Kubernetes "
"<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/"
"api-extension/custom-resources/\">自定义资源</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1249
msgid ""
"The <literal>UpgradePlan</literal> serves as an instruction mechanism for "
"the Upgrade Controller and it supports the following configurations:"
msgstr "<literal>UpgradePlan</literal> 是升级控制器的指令机制，支持以下配置："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1250
msgid ""
"<literal>releaseVersion</literal> - Edge release version to which the "
"cluster should be upgraded to. The release version must follow <link xl:"
"href=\"https://semver.org\">semantic</link> versioning and should be "
"retrieved from the Release Notes (<xref linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>releaseVersion</literal> - 群集应升级到的 Edge 版本。"
"版本必须遵循<link xl:href=\"https://semver.org\""
">语义</link>版本规范，并且应从发行说明（<xref linkend=\"release-notes\""
"/>）中检索。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1251
msgid ""
"<literal>disableDrain</literal> - <emphasis role=\"strong\">Optional</"
"emphasis>; instructs the Upgrade Controller on whether to disable node <link "
"xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/"
"kubectl_drain/\">drains</link>. Useful for when you have workloads with "
"<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/run-application/configure-"
"pdb/\">Disruption Budgets</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>disableDrain</literal> - <emphasis role=\"strong\">可选</emphasis>；"
"指示升级控制器是否禁用节点<link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_drain/\""
">清空</link>。当您有具有<link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/run-application/configure-pdb/\""
">干扰预算</link>的工作负载时，可以用到。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1252
msgid "Example for control plane node drain disablement:"
msgstr "禁用控制平面节点清空的示例："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1253
msgid "Example for control plane and worker node drain disablement:"
msgstr "禁用控制平面和工作节点清空的示例："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1254
msgid ""
"<literal>helm</literal> - <emphasis role=\"strong\">Optional</emphasis>; "
"specifies additional values for components installed via Helm."
msgstr ""
"<literal>helm</literal> - <emphasis role=\"strong\">可选</emphasis>；为通过 "
"Helm 安装的组件指定其他值。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><warning><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1255
msgid ""
"It is only advised to use this field for values that are critical for "
"upgrades. Standard chart value updates should be performed after the "
"respective charts have been upgraded to the next version."
msgstr "建议仅将此字段用于对升级至关重要的值。标准 chart 值的更新应在相应 chart "
"升级到下一版本后进行。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1256
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1257
msgid "ReleaseManifest"
msgstr "ReleaseManifest"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1258
msgid ""
"The Upgrade Controller introduces a new Kubernetes <link xl:href=\"https://"
"kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/"
"\">custom resource</link> called a <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal>."
msgstr ""
"升级控制器引入了一个名为 <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> 的新 Kubernetes "
"<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/extend-kubernetes/"
"api-extension/custom-resources/\">自定义资源</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1259
msgid ""
"The <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> resource is created by the Upgrade "
"Controller and holds component data for <emphasis role=\"strong\">one</"
"emphasis> specific Edge release version. This means that each Edge release "
"version upgrade will be represented by a different <literal>ReleaseManifest</"
"literal> resource."
msgstr ""
"<literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> 资源由升级控制器创建，保存<emphasis role="
"\"strong\">一个</emphasis>特定 Edge 版本的组件数据。这意味着每个 Edge "
"版本升级都将由不同的 <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> 资源表示。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><warning><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1260
msgid ""
"The Release Manifest should always be created by the Upgrade Controller."
msgstr "ReleaseManifest 只能由升级控制器创建。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><warning><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1261
msgid ""
"It is not advisable to manually create or edit the <literal>ReleaseManifest</"
"literal> resources. Users that decide to do so should do this <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">at their own risk</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"不建议手动创建或编辑 <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> 资源，否则，"
"用户需<emphasis role=\"strong\">自行承担风险</emphasis>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1262
msgid ""
"Component data that the Release Manifest ships include, but is not limited "
"to:"
msgstr "版本清单附带的组件数据包括但不限于："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1263
msgid ""
"Operating System data - version, supported architectures, additional upgrade "
"data, etc."
msgstr "操作系统数据 - 版本、支持的体系结构、其他升级数据等"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1264
msgid ""
"Kubernetes distribution data - <link xl:href=\"https://docs.rke2.io\">RKE2</"
"link>/<link xl:href=\"https://k3s.io\">K3s</link> supported versions"
msgstr ""
"Kubernetes 发行版数据 - <link xl:href=\"https://docs.rke2.io\">RKE2</link>/"
"<link xl:href=\"https://k3s.io\">K3s</link> 支持的版本"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1265
msgid ""
"Additional components data - SUSE Helm chart data (location, version, name, "
"etc.)"
msgstr "其他组件数据 - SUSE Helm chart 数据（位置、版本、名称等）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1266
msgid ""
"For an example of how a Release Manifest can look, refer to the <link xl:"
"href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/upgrade-controller/blob/main/config/"
"samples/lifecycle_v1alpha1_releasemanifest.yaml\">upstream</link> "
"documentation. <emphasis>Please note that this is just an example and it is "
"not intended to be created as a valid <literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> "
"resource.</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"有关版本清单的示例，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/"
"upgrade-controller/blob/main/config/samples/"
"lifecycle_v1alpha1_releasemanifest.yaml\""
">上游</link>文档。<emphasis>请注意，这只是一个示例，不可用于创建为有效的 "
"<literal>ReleaseManifest</literal> 资源。</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1267
msgid "Tracking the upgrade process"
msgstr "跟踪升级过程"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1268
msgid ""
"This section serves as means to track and debug the upgrade process that the "
"Upgrade Controller initiates once the user creates an <literal>UpgradePlan</"
"literal> resource."
msgstr "本节介绍如何跟踪和调试升级控制器在用户创建 <literal>UpgradePlan</literal> "
"资源后启动的升级资源过程。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1269
msgid "General"
msgstr "常规"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1270
msgid ""
"General information about the state of the upgrade process can be viewed in "
"the Upgrade Plan’s status conditions."
msgstr "有关升级过程状态的一般信息，可以在升级计划的状态条件中查看。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1271
msgid "The Upgrade Plan resource’s status can be viewed in the following way:"
msgstr "可以通过以下方式查看升级计划资源的状态："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><formalpara><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1272
msgid "Running Upgrade Plan example:"
msgstr "升级计划运行示例："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1273
msgid ""
"Here you can view every component that the Upgrade Controller will try to "
"schedule an upgrade for. Each condition follows the below template:"
msgstr "通过这种方式，您可以查看升级控制器将尝试安排升级的每个组件。每个条件都采用以"
"下模板："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1274
msgid ""
"<literal>lastTransitionTime</literal> - the last time that this component "
"condition has transitioned from one status to another."
msgstr "<literal>lastTransitionTime</literal> - 此组件条件上一次改变状态的时间。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1275
msgid ""
"<literal>message</literal> - message that indicates the current upgrade "
"state of the specific component condition."
msgstr "<literal>message</literal> - 指示特定组件条件当前升级状态的消息。"

