"documentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"然而，这种方法存在一定的局限性，特别是无法使用 Helm 升级此目录中的 "
"CRD。有关详细信息，请参见 <link xl:href=\"https://helm.sh/docs/"
"chart_best_practices/custom_resource_definitions/#some-caveats-and-"
"explanations\">Helm 文档</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1687
msgid ""
"As a result, before upgrading Metal<superscript>3</superscript> to an "
"<literal>Edge 3.2.0</literal> compatible version, users must manually "
"upgrade the underlying BMO CRDs."
