#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1776
msgid "OS upgrade (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade\"/>)"
msgstr "操作系统升级（<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade\"/>）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1777
msgid ""
"Kubernetes version upgrade (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-"
"upgrade\"/>)"
msgstr "Kubernetes 版本升级（<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade\"/>）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1778
msgid ""
"Helm chart upgrade (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade\"/>)"
msgstr "Helm chart 升级（<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade\"/>）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1779 l10n/source/edge.xml:2287
msgid "OS upgrade"
msgstr "操作系统升级"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1780 l10n/source/edge.xml:2288
msgid ""
"This section describes how to perform an operating system upgrade using "
"<xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/> and the <xref linkend=\"components-"
"system-upgrade-controller\"/>."
msgstr ""
"本节介绍如何使用<xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>和<xref linkend"
"=\"components-system-upgrade-controller\"/>执行操作系统升级。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1782
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-components\"/> - additional "
"components used by the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-components\"/> - "
"升级过程使用的其他组件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1783
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-overview\"/> - overview of "
"the upgrade process."
msgstr "<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-overview\"/> - "
"升级过程概述。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1784
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-requirements\"/> - "
"requirements of the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-requirements\"/> - "
"升级过程的要求。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1785
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment\"/> - "
"information on how to deploy <literal>SUC plans</literal>, responsible for "
"triggering the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment\"/> - "
"关于如何部署负责触发升级过程的 <literal>SUC 计划</literal>的信息。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1787
msgid ""
"This section covers the custom components that the <literal>OS upgrade</"
"literal> process uses over the default \"Day 2\" components (<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-components\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"本节介绍<literal>操作系统升级</literal>过程中使用的自定义组件，这些组件与默认"
"“Day 2”组件（<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-components\"/>）不同。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1788 l10n/source/edge.xml:2296
msgid "systemd.service"
msgstr "systemd.service"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1789 l10n/source/edge.xml:2297
msgid ""
"The OS upgrade on a specific node is handled by a <link xl:href=\"https://"
"www.freedesktop.org/software/systemd/man/latest/systemd.service."
"html\">systemd.service</link>."
msgstr ""
"特定节点上的操作系统升级由 <link xl:href=\"https://www.freedesktop.org/"
"software/systemd/man/latest/systemd.service.html\">systemd.service</link> "
"处理。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1790 l10n/source/edge.xml:2298
msgid ""
"A different service is created depending on what type of upgrade the OS "
"requires from one Edge version to another:"
msgstr "根据 Edge 版本升级时操作系统所需的不同升级类型，会创建不同的服务："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1791 l10n/source/edge.xml:2299
msgid ""
"For Edge versions that require the same OS version (e.g. <literal>6.0</"
"literal>), the <literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal> will be created. It "
"uses <link xl:href=\"https://kubic.opensuse.org/documentation/man-pages/"
"transactional-update.8.html\">transactional-update</link> to perform a <link "
"xl:href=\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:"
"Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\">normal package upgrade</link>."
msgstr ""
"对于需要相同操作系统版本（如 <literal>6.0</literal>）的 Edge 版本，将创建 "
"<literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal>。它使用 <link xl:href=\"https://"
"kubic.opensuse.org/documentation/man-pages/transactional-update.8.html\""
">transactional-update</link> 执行<link xl:href="
"\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\""
">常规软件包升级</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1792 l10n/source/edge.xml:2300
msgid ""
"For Edge versions that require an OS version migration (e.g <literal>5.5</"
"literal> → <literal>6.0</literal>), the <literal>os-migration.service</"
"literal> will be created. It uses <link xl:href=\"https://kubic.opensuse.org/"
"documentation/man-pages/transactional-update.8.html\">transactional-update</"
"link> to perform:"
msgstr ""
"对于需要迁移操作系统版本（例如 <literal>5.5</literal> → "
"<literal>6.0</literal>）的 Edge 版本，将创建 <literal>os-"
"migration.service</literal>。它使用 <link xl:href=\"https://"
"kubic.opensuse.org/documentation/man-pages/transactional-update.8.html\""
">transactional-update</link> 来执行："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1793 l10n/source/edge.xml:2301
msgid ""
"A <link xl:href=\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:"
"Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\">normal package upgrade</link> which ensures "
"that all packages are at up-to-date in order to mitigate any failures in the "
"migration related to old package versions."
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:Zypper_usage#Updating_packages\""
">常规软件包升级</link>，这可确保所有软件包均为最新版本，以减少因软件包版本过"
"旧而导致的迁移失败情况。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1794 l10n/source/edge.xml:2302
msgid ""
"An OS migration by utilizing the <literal>zypper migration</literal> command."
msgstr "利用 <literal>zypper migration</literal> 命令进行操作系统迁移。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1795
msgid ""
"The services mentioned above are shipped on each node through a <literal>SUC "
"plan</literal> which must be located on the management cluster that is in "
"need of an OS upgrade."
msgstr "上述服务通过 <literal>SUC "
"计划</literal>部署到每个节点，该计划必须位于需要升级操作系统的管理群集上。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1796 l10n/source/edge.xml:1914
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2149 l10n/source/edge.xml:2304
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2419 l10n/source/edge.xml:2645
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1797
msgid ""
"The upgrade of the operating system for management cluster nodes is done by "
"utilizing <literal>Fleet</literal> and the <literal>System Upgrade "
"Controller (SUC)</literal>."
msgstr ""
"通过 <literal>Fleet</literal> 和<literal>系统升级控制器 (SUC)</literal> "
"来为管理群集节点升级操作系统。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1798 l10n/source/edge.xml:2306
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Fleet</emphasis> is used to deploy and manage "
"<literal>SUC plans</literal> onto the desired cluster."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Fleet</emphasis> 用于将 <literal>SUC "
"计划</literal>部署到目标群集并对其进行管理。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1799 l10n/source/edge.xml:2307
msgid ""
"<literal>SUC plans</literal> are <link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/"
"concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/\">custom "
"resources</link> that describe the steps that <literal>SUC</literal> needs "
"to follow in order for a specific task to be executed on a set of nodes. For "
"an example of how an <literal>SUC plan</literal> looks like, refer to the "
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-upgrade-controller?"
"tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">upstream repository</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>SUC 计划</literal>是一种<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/"
"concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/\""
">自定义资源</link>，描述了 <literal>SUC</literal> "
"为在一组节点上执行特定任务而需要遵循的步骤。有关 <literal>SUC "
"计划</literal>的示例，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/"
"system-upgrade-controller?tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\""
">上游储存库</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1800 l10n/source/edge.xml:2308
msgid ""
"The <literal>OS SUC plans</literal> are shipped to each cluster by deploying "
"a <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add\">GitRepo</link> or "
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">Bundle</link> resource "
"to a specific Fleet <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/"
"namespaces#gitrepos-bundles-clusters-clustergroups\">workspace</link>. Fleet "
"retrieves the deployed <literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> and deploys its "
"contents (the <literal>OS SUC plans</literal>) to the desired cluster(s)."
msgstr ""
"通过向特定 Fleet <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/namespaces"
"#gitrepos-bundles-clusters-clustergroups\">工作区</link>部署 <link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add\">GitRepo</link> 或<link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">捆绑包</link>资源将<literal>操作系统 "
"SUC 计划</literal>分发到各个群集。Fleet 会获取已部署的 <literal>GitRepo/"
"捆绑包</literal>，并将其内容（<literal>操作系统 SUC "
"计划</literal>）部署到目标群集。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1801 l10n/source/edge.xml:1919
msgid ""
"<literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> resources are always deployed on the "
"<literal>management cluster</literal>. Whether to use a <literal>GitRepo</"
"literal> or <literal>Bundle</literal> resource depends on your use-case, "
"check <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\"/> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"<literal>GitRepo/"
"捆绑包</literal>资源始终部署在<literal>管理群集</literal>上。使用 "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> "
"还是<literal>捆绑包</literal>资源取决于具体应用场景，有关详细信息，"
"请参见<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1802 l10n/source/edge.xml:2310
msgid "<literal>OS SUC plans</literal> describe the following workflow:"
msgstr "<literal>操作系统 SUC 计划</literal>描述了以下工作流程："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1803 l10n/source/edge.xml:2311
msgid ""
"Always <link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/"
"generated/kubectl_cordon/\">cordon</link> the nodes before OS upgrades."
msgstr ""
"执行操作系统升级前，务必要<link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_cordon/\""
">封锁</link>节点。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1804 l10n/source/edge.xml:1922
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2312 l10n/source/edge.xml:2427
msgid ""
"Always upgrade <literal>control-plane</literal> nodes before "
"<literal>worker</literal> nodes."
msgstr "务必先升级<literal>控制平面</literal>节点，再升级<literal>工作</literal>节点"
"。"

