"examples</literal> <link xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases\">版本</link>的正确 "
"Fleet。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1830 l10n/source/edge.xml:1951
