#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1915
msgid ""
"The Kubernetes distribution upgrade for management cluster nodes is done by "
"utilizing <literal>Fleet</literal> and the <literal>System Upgrade "
"Controller (SUC)</literal>."
msgstr ""
"通过 <literal>Fleet</literal> 和<literal>系统升级控制器 (SUC)</literal> "
"来为管理群集节点升级 Kubernetes 发行版。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1916 l10n/source/edge.xml:2421
msgid ""
"<literal>Fleet</literal> is used to deploy and manage <literal>SUC plans</"
"literal> onto the desired cluster."
msgstr "<literal>Fleet</literal> 用于将 <literal>SUC "
"计划</literal>部署到目标群集并对其进行管理。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1917 l10n/source/edge.xml:2422
msgid ""
"<literal>SUC plans</literal> are <link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/"
"concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/\">custom "
"resources</link> that describe the steps that <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</"
"emphasis> needs to follow in order for a specific task to be executed on a "
"set of nodes. For an example of how an <literal>SUC plan</literal> looks "
"like, refer to the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/system-upgrade-"
"controller?tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\">upstream repository</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>SUC 计划</literal>是一种<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/"
"concepts/extend-kubernetes/api-extension/custom-resources/"
"\">自定义资源</link>，描述了 <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> "
"为在一组节点上执行特定任务而需要遵循的步骤。有关 <literal>SUC "
"计划</literal>的示例，请参见<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/"
"system-upgrade-controller?tab=readme-ov-file#example-plans\""
">上游储存库</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1918 l10n/source/edge.xml:2423
msgid ""
"The <literal>K8s SUC plans</literal> are shipped on each cluster by "
"deploying a <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add\">GitRepo</"
"link> or <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">Bundle</link> "
"resource to a specific Fleet <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/"
"namespaces#gitrepos-bundles-clusters-clustergroups\">workspace</link>. Fleet "
"retrieves the deployed <literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> and deploys its "
"contents (the <literal>K8s SUC plans</literal>) to the desired cluster(s)."
msgstr ""
"通过向特定 Fleet <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/namespaces"
"#gitrepos-bundles-clusters-clustergroups\">工作区</link>部署 <link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-add\">GitRepo</link> 或<link xl:href="
"\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">捆绑包</link>资源将 <literal>K8s SUC "
"计划</literal>分发到各个群集。Fleet 会获取已部署的 <literal>GitRepo/"
"捆绑包</literal>，并将其内容（<literal>K8s SUC "
"计划</literal>）部署到目标群集。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1920 l10n/source/edge.xml:2425
msgid "<literal>K8s SUC plans</literal> describe the following workflow:"
msgstr "<literal>K8s SUC 计划</literal>描述了以下工作流程："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1921 l10n/source/edge.xml:2426
msgid ""
"Always <link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/"
"generated/kubectl_cordon/\">cordon</link> the nodes before K8s upgrades."
msgstr ""
"执行 K8s 升级前，务必要<link xl:href="
"\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/kubectl/generated/kubectl_cordon/\""
">封锁</link>节点。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1923 l10n/source/edge.xml:2428
msgid ""
"Always upgrade the <literal>control-plane</literal> nodes <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">one</emphasis> node at a time and the <literal>worker</"
"literal> nodes <emphasis role=\"strong\">two</emphasis> nodes at a time."
msgstr ""
"始终一次升级<emphasis role=\"strong\""
">一个</emphasis><literal>控制平面</literal>节点，一次升级<emphasis role="
"\"strong\">两个</emphasis><literal>工作</literal>节点。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1924 l10n/source/edge.xml:2429
msgid ""
"Once the <literal>K8s SUC plans</literal> are deployed, the workflow looks "
"like this:"
msgstr "部署 <literal>K8s SUC 计划</literal>后，工作流程如下："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1925 l10n/source/edge.xml:2430
msgid ""
"SUC reconciles the deployed <literal>K8s SUC plans</literal> and creates a "
"<literal>Kubernetes Job</literal> on <emphasis role=\"strong\">each node</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"SUC 协调已部署的 <literal>K8s SUC 计划</literal>，并在<emphasis role="
"\"strong\">每个节点</emphasis>上创建一个 <literal>Kubernetes 作业</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1926
msgid ""
"Depending on the Kubernetes distribution, the Job will create a Pod that "
"runs either the rke2-upgrade (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-"
"upgrade-components-rke2-upgrade\"/>) or the k3s-upgrade (<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-components-k3s-upgrade\"/>) "
"container image."
msgstr ""
"根据 Kubernetes 发行版的不同，该作业将创建一个运行 rke2-upgrade（<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-components-rke2-upgrade\"/>）或 "
"k3s-upgrade（<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-components-"
"k3s-upgrade\"/>）容器映像的 Pod。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1927 l10n/source/edge.xml:2432
msgid "The created Pod will go through the following workflow:"
msgstr "创建的 Pod 将执行以下工作流程："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1928 l10n/source/edge.xml:2433
msgid ""
"Replace the existing <literal>rke2/k3s</literal> binary on the node with the "
"one from the <literal>rke2-upgrade/k3s-upgrade</literal> image."
msgstr ""
"用 <literal>rke2-upgrade/k3s-upgrade</literal> "
"映像中的二进制文件替换节点上现有的 <literal>rke2/k3s</literal> 二进制文件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1929 l10n/source/edge.xml:2434
msgid "Kill the running <literal>rke2/k3s</literal> process."
msgstr "终止正在运行的 <literal>rke2/k3s</literal> 进程。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1930 l10n/source/edge.xml:2435
msgid ""
"Killing the <literal>rke2/k3s</literal> process triggers a restart, "
"launching a new process that runs the updated binary, resulting in an "
"upgraded Kubernetes distribution version."
msgstr ""
"终止 <literal>rke2/k3s</literal> "
"进程会触发重启，启动运行已更新二进制文件的新进程，从而实现 Kubernetes "
"发行版版本的升级。"

