#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2750
msgid ""
"SUSE Edge for Telco (formerly known as Adaptive Telco Infrastructure "
"Platform/ATIP) is a Telco-optimized edge computing platform that enables "
"telecom companies to innovate and accelerate the modernization of their "
"networks."
msgstr ""
"SUSE Edge for "
"Telco（以前称为“自适应电信基础架构平台”(ATIP)）是针对电信行业进行优化的边缘计"
"算平台，可帮助电信公司实现创新并加速其网络的现代化改造。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2751
msgid ""
"SUSE Edge for Telco is a complete Telco cloud stack for hosting CNFs such as "
"5G Packet Core and Cloud RAN."
msgstr "SUSE Edge for Telco 是一个完整的电信云堆栈，可承载 5G "
"分组核心网和云化无线接入网等容器化网络功能 (CNF)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2752
msgid ""
"Automates zero-touch rollout and lifecycle management of complex edge stack "
"configurations at Telco scale."
msgstr "能实现电信级规模下复杂边缘堆栈配置的零接触部署及生命周期管理自动化。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2753
msgid ""
"Continuously assures quality on Telco-grade hardware, using Telco-specific "
"configurations and workloads."
msgstr "借助电信专用配置与工作负载，在电信级硬件上持续保障质量。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2754
msgid ""
"Consists of components that are purpose-built for the edge and hence have "
"smaller footprint and higher performance per Watt."
msgstr "其组件专为边缘场景打造，因此资源占用更少，并且性能功耗比更高。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2755
