"<literal>v1.31.7+rke2r1</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3481
msgid ""
"The <literal>image</literal> to be used as a reference to the image "
"generated using <literal>EIB</literal> on the previous section (<xref "
