#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3484
msgid "Advanced Network Configuration"
msgstr "高级网络配置"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3485
msgid ""
"The directed network provisioning workflow allows for specific network "
"configurations in downstream clusters, such as static IPs, bonding, VLANs, "
"IPv6, etc."
msgstr "定向网络置备工作流程允许在下游群集中使用静态 IP、绑定、VLAN 等网络配置。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3486
msgid ""
"The following sections describe the additional steps required to enable "
"provisioning downstream clusters using advanced network configuration."
msgstr "以下章节将介绍使用高级网络配置置备下游群集需额外执行的步骤。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3488
msgid ""
"The image generated using <literal>EIB</literal> has to include the network "
"folder and the script following this section (<xref linkend=\"add-network-"
"eib\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"使用 <literal>EIB</literal> 生成的映像必须包含<xref linkend=\"add-network-"
"eib\"/>一节中所述的 network 文件夹和脚本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3489 l10n/source/edge.xml:3523
msgid "<emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3490
msgid ""
"Before proceeding refer to one of the following sections for guidance on the "
"steps required to enroll and provision the host(s):"
msgstr "在继续操作之前，请参考以下章节，了解登记和置备主机所需执行的步骤："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3491 l10n/source/edge.xml:3525
msgid ""
"Downstream cluster provisioning with Directed network provisioning (single-"
"node) (<xref linkend=\"single-node\"/>)"
msgstr "使用定向网络置备来置备下游群集（单节点）（<xref linkend=\"single-node\"/>）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3492 l10n/source/edge.xml:3526
msgid ""
"Downstream cluster provisioning with Directed network provisioning (multi-"
"node) (<xref linkend=\"multi-node\"/>)"
msgstr "使用定向网络置备来置备下游群集（多节点）（<xref linkend=\"multi-node\"/>）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3493
msgid ""
"Any advanced network configuration must be applied at enrollment time "
"through the <literal>BareMetalHost</literal> host definition and an "
"associated Secret containing an <literal>nmstate</literal> formatted "
"<literal>networkData</literal> block. The following example file defines a "
"secret containing the required <literal>networkData</literal> that requests "
"a static <literal>IP</literal> and <literal>VLAN</literal> for the "
"downstream cluster host:"
msgstr ""
"任何高级网络配置都必须在登记时通过 <literal>BareMetalHost</literal> "
"主机定义以及包含 <literal>nmstate</literal> 格式 <literal>networkData</"
"literal> 块的关联机密来应用。以下示例文件定义了一个包含所需 "
"<literal>networkData</literal> 的机密，该机密会为下游群集主机请求静态 "
"<literal>IP</literal> 和 <literal>VLAN</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3494
msgid ""
"As you can see, the example shows the configuration to enable the interface "
"with static IPs, as well as the configuration to enable the VLAN using the "
"base interface, once the following variables are replaced with the actual "
"values, according to your infrastructure:"
msgstr ""
"如您所见，该示例展示了启用配备静态 IP 的接口的配置，以及使用基础接口启用 "
"VLAN 的配置，在实际应用时，需根据您的基础架构将以下变量替换为实际值："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3495
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_INTERFACE}</literal> — The control-plane interface "
"to be used for the edge cluster (for example, <literal>eth0</literal>). "
"Including <literal>identifier: mac-address</literal> the naming is inspected "
"automatically by the MAC address so any interface name can be used."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_INTERFACE}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的控制平面接口（"
"例如 <literal>eth0</literal>）。如果包含 <literal>identifier: mac-"
"address</literal>，系统将会根据 MAC "
"地址自动检测命名，因此可以使用任何接口名称。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3496
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_IP}</literal> — The IP address to be used as an "
"endpoint for the edge cluster (must match with the kubeapi-server endpoint)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_IP}</literal> — 用作边缘群集端点的 IP 地址（必须与 "
"kubeapi-server 端点匹配）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3497
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_PREFIX}</literal> — The CIDR to be used for the "
"edge cluster (for example, <literal>24</literal> if you want <literal>/24</"
"literal> or <literal>255.255.255.0</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_PREFIX}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的 CIDR（例如，"
"如果您要使用 <literal>/24</literal> 子网掩码，请指定 <literal>24</literal>；"
"也可以指定 <literal>255.255.255.0</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3498
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_GATEWAY}</literal> — The gateway to be used for the "
"edge cluster (for example, <literal>192.168.100.1</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_GATEWAY}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的网关（例如 "
"<literal>192.168.100.1</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3499
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_MAC}</literal> — The MAC address to be used for the "
"control-plane interface (for example, <literal>00:0c:29:3e:3e:3e</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE1_MAC}</literal> — 用于控制平面接口的 MAC 地址（例如 "
"<literal>00:0c:29:3e:3e:3e</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3500
msgid ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER}</literal> — The DNS to be used for the edge cluster "
"(for example, <literal>192.168.100.2</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的 DNS（例如 "
"<literal>192.168.100.2</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3501
msgid ""
"<literal>${VLAN_ID}</literal> — The VLAN ID to be used for the edge cluster "
"(for example, <literal>100</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${VLAN_ID}</literal> — 用于边缘群集的 VLAN ID（例如 "
"<literal>100</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3502
msgid ""
"Any other <literal>nmstate</literal>-compliant definition can be used to "
"configure the network for the downstream cluster to adapt to the specific "
"requirements. For example, it is possible to specify a static dual-stack "
"configuration:"
msgstr ""
"任何其他符合 <literal>nmstate</literal> "
"标准的定义都可用于配置下游群集的网络，以适应特定要求。例如，可以指定静态双栈"
"配置："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3503
msgid ""
"As for the previous example, replace the following variables with actual "
"values, according to your infrastructure:"
msgstr "与前面的示例一样，请根据您的基础架构将以下变量替换为实际值："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3504
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_IP_V4}</literal> - the IPv4 address to assign to the "
"host"
msgstr "<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_IP_V4}</literal> - 分配给主机的 IPv4 地址"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3505
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_PREFIX_V4}</literal> - the IPv4 prefix of the "
"network to which the host IP belongs"
msgstr "<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_PREFIX_V4}</literal> - 主机 IP 所属网络的 IPv4 前缀"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3506
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_IP_V6}</literal> - the IPv6 address to assign to the "
"host"
msgstr "<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_IP_V6}</literal> - 分配给主机的 IPv6 地址"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3507
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_PREFIX_V6}</literal> - the IPv6 prefix of the "
"network to which the host IP belongs"
msgstr "<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_PREFIX_V6}</literal> - 主机 IP 所属网络的 IPv6 前缀"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3508
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_GATEWAY_V4}</literal> - the IPv4 address of the "
"gateway for the traffic matching the default route"
msgstr "<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_GATEWAY_V4}</literal> - "
"与默认路由匹配的流量所用网关的 IPv4 地址"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3509
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_GATEWAY_V6}</literal> - the IPv6 address of the "
"gateway for the traffic matching the default route"
msgstr "<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_GATEWAY_V6}</literal> - "
"与默认路由匹配的流量所用网关的 IPv6 地址"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3510
msgid ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_INTERFACE}</literal> - the name of the interface to "
"assign the addresses to and to use for egress traffic matching the default "
"route, for both IPv4 and IPv6"
msgstr ""
"<literal>${CONTROLPLANE_INTERFACE}</literal> - "
"地址要分配到的接口的名称，该接口同时供与默认路由匹配的出站流量使用（适用于 "
"IPv4 和 IPv6）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3511
msgid ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER_V4}</literal> and/or <literal>${DNS_SERVER_V6}</"
"literal> - the IP address(es) of the DNS server(s) to use, which can be "
"specified as single or multiple entries. Both IPv4 and/or IPv6 addresses are "
"supported"
msgstr ""
"<literal>${DNS_SERVER_V4}</literal> 和/或 <literal>${DNS_SERVER_V6}</"
"literal> - 要使用的 DNS 服务器的 IP 地址（可指定单项或多项，支持 IPv4 和/或 "
"IPv6 地址）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3513
msgid ""
"You can refer to <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/atip/tree/main/"
"telco-examples/edge-clusters\">the SUSE Edge for Telco examples repo</link> "
"for more complex examples, including IPv6 only and dual-stack configurations."
msgstr ""
"有关更复杂的示例（包括仅支持 IPv6 的配置和双栈配置），您可以参考 <link "
"xl:href="
"\"https://github.com/suse-edge/atip/tree/main/telco-examples/edge-clusters\""
">SUSE Edge for Telco 示例代码库</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3514
msgid ""
"Lastly, regardless of the network configuration details, ensure that the "
"secret is referenced by appending <literal>preprovisioningNetworkDataName</"
"literal> to the <literal>BaremetalHost</literal> object to successfully "
"enroll the host in the management cluster."
msgstr ""
"最后，无论网络配置详细信息如何，都要确保通过在 <literal>BaremetalHost</"
"literal> 对象中附加 <literal>preprovisioningNetworkDataName</literal> "
"来引用该机密，以便成功在管理群集中登记主机。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3515
msgid ""
"If you need to deploy a multi-node cluster, the same process must be done "
"for each node."
msgstr "如果需要部署多节点群集，必须对每个节点执行相同的过程。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3516
msgid ""
"The <literal>Metal3DataTemplate</literal>, <literal>networkData</literal> "
"and <literal>Metal3 IPAM</literal> are currently not supported; only the "
"configuration via static secrets is fully supported."
msgstr ""
"目前不支持 <literal>Metal3DataTemplate</literal>、<literal>networkData</"
"literal> 和 <literal>Metal3 "
"IPAM</literal>；只有通过静态机密进行的配置才完全受支持。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3517
msgid "Telco features (DPDK, SR-IOV, CPU isolation, huge pages, NUMA, etc.)"
msgstr "电信功能（DPDK、SR-IOV、CPU 隔离、大页、NUMA 等）"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3518
msgid ""
"The directed network provisioning workflow allows to automate the Telco "
"features to be used in the downstream clusters to run Telco workloads on top "
"of those servers."
msgstr "定向网络置备工作流程允许将下游群集中使用的电信功能自动化，以便在这些服务器上"
"运行电信工作负载。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3520
msgid ""
"The image generated using <literal>EIB</literal> has to include the specific "
"Telco packages following this section (<xref linkend=\"add-telco-feature-"
"eib\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"使用 <literal>EIB</literal> 生成的映像必须包含<xref linkend=\"add-telco-"
"feature-eib\"/>一节中所述的特定电信软件包。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3521
msgid ""
"The image generated using <literal>EIB</literal>, as described in the "
"previous section (<xref linkend=\"eib-edge-image-connected\"/>), has to be "
"located in the management cluster exactly on the path you configured on this "
"section (<xref linkend=\"metal3-media-server\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"如前面的章节（<xref linkend=\"eib-edge-image-connected\"/>）所述使用 "
"<literal>EIB</literal> 生成的映像必须位于管理群集上您按照<xref linkend="
"\"metal3-media-server\"/>一节所述配置的确切路径中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3524
msgid ""
"Use the following two sections as the base to enroll and provision the hosts:"
msgstr "基于以下两个章节的内容登记和置备主机："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3527
msgid "The Telco features covered in this section are the following:"
msgstr "本节将介绍以下电信功能："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3528
msgid "DPDK and VFs creation"
msgstr "DPDK 和 VF 创建"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3529
msgid "SR-IOV and VFs allocation to be used by the workloads"
msgstr "工作负载使用的 SR-IOV 和 VF 分配"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3530
msgid "CPU isolation and performance tuning"
msgstr "CPU 隔离和性能调优"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3531
msgid "Huge pages configuration"
msgstr "大页配置"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3532
msgid "Kernel parameters tuning"
msgstr "内核参数调优"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3533
msgid ""
"For more information about the Telco features, see <xref linkend=\"atip-"
"features\"/>."
msgstr "有关电信功能的详细信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"atip-features\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3534
msgid ""
"The changes required to enable the Telco features shown above are all inside "
"the <literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal> block in the provision file "
"<literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</literal>. The rest of the "
"information inside the file <literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</"
"literal> is the same as the information provided in the provisioning section "
"(<xref linkend=\"single-node-provision\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"启用上述电信功能所需做出的更改都可以在 <literal>capi-provisioning-"
"example.yaml</literal> 置备文件的 <literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal> "
"块中完成。<literal>capi-provisioning-example.yaml</literal> "
"文件中的其余信息与置备相关章节（<xref linkend=\"single-node-provision\""
"/>）中提供的信息相同。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3535
msgid ""
"To make the process clear, the changes required on that block "
"(<literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal>) to enable the Telco features are the "
"following:"
msgstr "明确地说，为启用电信功能而需在该块 (<literal>RKE2ControlPlane</literal>) "
"中进行的更改如下："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3536
msgid ""
"The <literal>preRKE2Commands</literal> to be used to execute the commands "
"before the <literal>RKE2</literal> installation process. In this case, use "
"the <literal>modprobe</literal> command to enable the <literal>vfio-pci</"
"literal> and the <literal>SR-IOV</literal> kernel modules."
msgstr ""
"指定 <literal>preRKE2Commands</literal>，该参数用于在 <literal>RKE2</"
"literal> 安装过程开始之前执行命令。本例使用 <literal>modprobe</literal> "
"命令启用 <literal>vfio-pci</literal> 和 <literal>SR-IOV</literal> 内核模块。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3537
msgid ""
"The ignition file <literal>/var/lib/rancher/rke2/server/manifests/configmap-"
"sriov-custom-auto.yaml</literal> to be used to define the interfaces, "
"drivers and the number of <literal>VFs</literal> to be created and exposed "
"to the workloads."
msgstr ""
"指定 ignition 文件 <literal>/var/lib/rancher/rke2/server/manifests/configmap-"
"sriov-custom-"
"auto.yaml</literal>，该文件用于定义要创建且向工作负载公开的接口、驱动程序及 "
"<literal>VF</literal> 数量。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3538
msgid ""
"The values inside the config map <literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</literal> "
"are the only values to be replaced with real values."
msgstr "只有 <literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</literal> "
"配置映射中的值可以替换为实际值。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3539
msgid ""
"<literal>${RESOURCE_NAME1}</literal> — The resource name to be used for the "
"first <literal>PF</literal> interface (for example, <literal>sriov-resource-"
"du1</literal>). It is added to the prefix <literal>rancher.io</literal> to "
"be used as a label to be used by the workloads (for example, "
"<literal>rancher.io/sriov-resource-du1</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${RESOURCE_NAME1}</literal> — 用于第一个 <literal>PF</literal> "
"接口的资源名称（例如 <literal>sriov-resource-du1</literal>）。它将添加到前缀 "
"<literal>rancher.io</literal> 的后面，供工作负载用作标签（例如 <literal>"
"rancher.io/sriov-resource-du1</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3540
msgid ""
"<literal>${SRIOV-NIC-NAME1}</literal> — The name of the first <literal>PF</"
"literal> interface to be used (for example, <literal>eth0</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${SRIOV-NIC-NAME1}</literal> — 要使用的第一个 <literal>PF</literal> "
"接口的名称（例如 <literal>eth0</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3541
msgid ""
"<literal>${PF_NAME1}</literal> — The name of the first physical function "
"<literal>PF</literal> to be used. Generate more complex filters using this "
"(for example, <literal>eth0#2-5</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${PF_NAME1}</literal> — 要使用的第一个物理功能 <literal>PF</"
"literal> 的名称。可以使用此名称生成更复杂的过滤器（例如 "
"<literal>eth0#2-5</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3542
msgid ""
"<literal>${DRIVER_NAME1}</literal> — The driver name to be used for the "
"first <literal>VF</literal> interface (for example, <literal>vfio-pci</"
"literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${DRIVER_NAME1}</literal> — 用于第一个 <literal>VF</literal> "
"接口的驱动程序名称（例如 <literal>vfio-pci</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3543
msgid ""
"<literal>${NUM_VFS1}</literal> — The number of <literal>VFs</literal> to be "
"created for the first <literal>PF</literal> interface (for example, "
"<literal>8</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${NUM_VFS1}</literal> — 要为第一个 <literal>PF</literal> 接口创建的 "
"<literal>VF</literal> 数量（例如 <literal>8</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3544
msgid ""
"The <literal>/var/sriov-auto-filler.sh</literal> to be used as a translator "
"between the high-level config map <literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</"
"literal> and the <literal>sriovnetworknodepolicy</literal> which contains "
"the low-level hardware information. This script has been created to abstract "
"the user from the complexity to know in advance the hardware information. No "
"changes are required in this file, but it should be present if we need to "
"enable <literal>sr-iov</literal> and create <literal>VFs</literal>."
msgstr ""
"提供 <literal>/var/sriov-auto-filler.sh</literal>，用作高层级配置映射 "
"<literal>sriov-custom-auto-config</literal> 与包含底层硬件信息的 "
"<literal>sriovnetworknodepolicy</literal> "
"之间的转换器。创建此脚本的目的是简化用户操作，让其无需提前了解复杂的硬件信息"
"。不需要在此文件中进行更改，但如果我们需要启用 <literal>sr-iov</literal> "
"并创建 <literal>VF</literal>，则应该提供此脚本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3545
msgid "The kernel arguments to be used to enable the following features:"
msgstr "用于启用以下功能的内核参数："

