#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3550
msgid "domain,nohz,managed_irq,1-30,33-62"
msgstr "domain,nohz,managed_irq,1-30,33-62"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3551
msgid "Isolate the cores 1-30 and 33-62."
msgstr "隔离核心 1-30 和 33-62。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3554
msgid ""
"Allows the kernel to skew the timer interrupts across the isolated CPUs."
msgstr "允许内核在隔离的 CPU 之间错开定时器中断。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3557
msgid ""
"Allows the kernel to run the timer tick on a single CPU when the system is "
"idle."
msgstr "允许内核在系统空闲时在单个 CPU 上运行定时器节拍周期。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3559 l10n/source/edge.xml:3562
msgid "1-30,33-62"
msgstr "1-30,33-62"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3563
msgid ""
"Allows the kernel to run the RCU callbacks on a single CPU when the system "
"is idle."
msgstr "允许内核在系统空闲时在单个 CPU 上运行 RCU 回调。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3565
msgid "0,31,32,63"
msgstr "0,31,32,63"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3566
msgid ""
"Allows the kernel to run the interrupts on a single CPU when the system is "
"idle."
msgstr "允许内核在系统空闲时在单个 CPU 上运行中断。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3569
msgid "Minimizes the latency of exiting the idle state."
msgstr "最大限度地减少因退出空闲状态造成的延迟。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3572
msgid "Allows to use vfio for the dpdk interfaces."
msgstr "允许为 dpdk 接口使用 vfio。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3575
msgid "Enables the use of vfio for VFs."
msgstr "允许为 VF 使用 vfio。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><informaltable><tgroup><tbody><row><entry><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3578
