msgstr "禁用 NMI 看门狗。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3590
msgid "The following systemd services are used to enable the following:"
msgstr "以下 systemd 服务用于启用下述功能："

